Class BoundedLinkedList<E>

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.Deque<E>, java.util.List<E>, java.util.Queue<E>

    public final class BoundedLinkedList<E>
extends java.util.LinkedList<E>
    A LinkedList version with a maximum number of elements. When adding elements to the end of the list, first elements in the list are discarded if the maximum size is reached.
    See Also:
